                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d416">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 702.6211/228.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Governor <persName type="from">Lister</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Olympia, Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-05-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 13, 1915</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Charges against German Consul and his Secretary filed in superior court, King
                    County, in which county Seattle is located, have been dismissed by the
                    prosecuting attorney of that county. This clears up the entire situation in
                    relation to Seattle matter.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Ernest Lister</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
